Function to recode position of height measurements variable

Source: R/09-recode_anthro.R
recode_position.Rd

Function to recode position of height measurements variable

recode_position(df)

Arguments

df

A coverage data.frame collected for the Liberia Coverage Survey

Value

A vector of recoded position of height measurements based on any re-testing done

Examples


recode_position(df = coverageData.r2)
